      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3039329/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3039329-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3039329/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">hsxtc</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-04-12"
      class="main-meta">2011-04-12 01:29:05</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4903874_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  《与社会学同游》有感  同样是对社会学概览性的图书，成书晚于《社会学的想象力》的《与社会学同游》，在国内的知名度远不及前者。其作者彼得伯格所著二十余本著作目前国内也仅译成三本。分析其原因可能有以下两点：第一，与国内社会学的发展阶段有关，社会学在国内学科基础仍...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">12有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4903874_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4903874_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










